OL,3,CWhat did the government know and when
OL,4,Cabout Mandelson and Epstein?
OL,6,FThe sacking of Peter Mandelson as US
OL,7,Fambassador is yet another
OL,8,Fembarrassment for Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Ffollowing the departure of Angela
OL,10,FRayner last week.
OL,12,FThe PM's judgement has once again been
OL,13,Fcalled into question, as Mandelson's
OL,14,Ffriendship with Epstein was well known
OL,15,Fprior to his appointment in February
OL,16,Fthis year.
OL,18,FMandelson's sacking couldn't come at a
OL,19,Fworse time for the prime minister,
OL,20,Fwith President Trump due to arrive in
OL,21,Fthe UK for a state visit next week.
