OL,3,CWhat did the government know and when
OL,4,Cabout Mandelson and Epstein?
OL,6,FThe government said it sacked the US
OL,7,Fambassador because the emails released
OL,8,Fby Bloomberg and The Sun on Wednesday
OL,9,Fnight showed "the depth and extent of
OL,10,FMandelson's relationship with Jeffrey
OL,11,FEpstein is materially different from
OL,12,Fthat known at the time of his
OL,13,Fappointment."
OL,15,FITV News understands the government
OL,16,Fdid not have access to the emails at
OL,17,Fthe time of Mandelson's appointment as
OL,18,Fambassador, nor did Mandelson himself,
OL,19,Fas they were sent from a long-closed
OL,20,Femail address.
