OL,3,CWhat did the government know and when
OL,4,Cabout Mandelson and Epstein?
OL,6,FEpstein was convicted of child sex
OL,7,Foffences in 2008 and sentenced to 18
OL,8,Fmonths in jail. While the emails
OL,9,Freleased on Wednesday lay bare
OL,10,FMandelson's explicit support for
OL,11,FEsptein, the public already knew
OL,12,FMandelson stayed at the financier's
OL,13,Fhouse during his prison sentence.
OL,15,FA report released in 2023 showed
OL,16,Femails between Epstein and his private
OL,17,Fbanker at JP Morgan, in which Epstein
OL,18,Fwrites, "Peter will be staying at 71st
OL,19,Fover weekend."
